
= Some Mental Models

== Frustration is part of the game

Frustration is natural when you start programming in R because it is such a stickler for punctuation, and even one character out of place can cause it to complain. But while you should expect to be a little frustrated, take comfort in that this experience is typical and temporary: it happens to everyone, and the only way to get over it is to keep trying.

== The Non-linear Nature of Data Science

In reality, *Data Science* is not sequential from 1 to 5. Rather, it is continuous process of planning, doing, reviewing, and improving.

