== Informed Decision-making

#figure(
  image("/assets/02/ds_intro/map_is_not_territory.png", width: 60%),
  caption: [The Map is not the Territory],
)

Informed decisions require alignment of both:
+ *External*: reality (the territory)
+ *Internal*: perception of reality (the map); i.e., the data we collect and analyze
